 "Route Advisor ⊣ Waste Operations Governor, langgraph-clj StateGraph,
 append-only audit ledger. A municipal waste-collection ROUTE
 DISPATCH COORDINATION actor -- not direct collection-robot/vehicle
 control authority and not a municipal diversion-rate compliance
 authority. Four ops (`:log-route-pickup` / `:log-sorting-result` /
 `:schedule-route-dispatch` / `:escalate-contamination`), all
 `:effect :propose` only. Ten concrete governor checks elaborate this
 blueprint's HARD invariants: propose-only effect, closed op
 allowlist, closed proposal-effect allowlist (no direct
